vector-skin-desc:
Tere victor eŋgama 2:
* 2011 -A monobook ziyuo vɛɛseŋ ne kaa paala ane tontoŋ yaga baabo.
* 2022 - A vector meɛbo naŋ paale a WMF   kyɛllɛ [[mw:Desktop Improvements]] toma.
prefs-vector-enable-vector-1-help: Yuomo naŋ waana, te na apdeetiri la Victor Skin beɛlɛ beɛlɛ. legacy victor na ko fo la sori ka fo kaa Victor vɛɛseŋ koroo (a ŋa disembare 2019). Ka fõõ boɔra ka fo zanne yɛlɛ yaga kyaare a apdeeti, gaa te  [[mw:Reading/Web/Desktop_Improvements|project page]].
vector-opt-out-tooltip: Leɛre a fo sɛgeroo na leɛ gaa a eŋgane zi koraa (legacy vector)
vector-language-button-aria-label: Gaa atekele Kɔkɔ yuo poɔ. A be la {{PLURAL:$1|$1 language|$1 kɔkɔɛ}}
vector-no-language-button-aria-label: Atekele ŋa be la a kɔkɔre ŋa yoŋ poɔ. Paale a atekele ko kɔkɔ yobo
vector-language-redirect-to-top: Kɔkɔɛ liŋkere be la a peegyi sazu yaare yi yelzu.
vector-anon-user-menu-pages: Peegyiri ko kpɛ yi maale enneba
vector-anon-user-menu-pages-label: Zanne yɛlɛ yaga kyaare maale eŋ
vector-limited-width-toggle-on-popup: Fo kyɔŋe la fo nare bimmu eŋ yaloŋ gbuli. Ka fõõ na Leɛ gaa a yaloŋ fẽẽ zie, neɛ a tombiri.
vector-limited-width-toggle-off-popup: Fo na baŋ ŋmɛɛle yi la yaloŋ figiraa ane yaloŋ gbuli kpakyaga ka fõõ neɛ a tombiri ŋa.
vector-prefs-limited-width-help: Eŋ figibo yaloŋ waaloŋ ko baabo kannoo daŋyaabo.
empty-language-selector-body: Peegyi yelbulo ba taa teɛbo Kɔkɔ yobo poɔ.
vector-toc-unpinned-popup: A yɛlɛ yelzu tage gaa la a kyɛ.
vector-page-tools-unpinned-popup: A tonton boma tage gaa la a kyɛ.
vector-main-menu-unpinned-popup: A yɛlɛ yelzu tage gaa la a kyɛ.
vector-readability-survey-description: Wulɔ ka wikipiideɛ poɔ sɛgre was ko fo? De a puli bone a daa o eŋ. Zanne yɛlɛ yaga kyaare neŋ [[mw:Special:MyLanguage/Reading/Web/Accessibility for reading|Accessibility for reading project]].
vector-readability-survey-optout: Neɛ tombiri a de bomaale eŋ bee tere kyɛ tere fo teɛroo kyaare ne a gampɛle tuuro. [[#close-vector-survey|Remove this tool]].
